James Cameron's Avatar: The Game is the official video game based on the
  highly anticipated film James Cameron's Avatar.  The video game will take you
  deep into the heart of Pandora, an alien planet that is beyond imagination.
  Gamers will encounter the Na'vi, Pandora's indigenous people and discover
  other life forms the likes of which have never been seen in the world of
  video games before.  When conflict erupts between the RDA Corporation, a
  space-faring consortium in search of valuable resources, and the Na'vi,
  gamers will find themselves thrust into a fight for the heart of a planet and
  the fate of a civilization.
